<view class="page">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="logo-wrapper">
      <view class="logo">
        <text class="logo-icon">🍽️</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <text class="app-name">美食菜谱</text>
    <text class="version">版本 v{{version}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">
      <text class="title-icon">ℹ️</text>
      <text class="title-text">关于我们</text>
    </view>
    
    <view class="intro-box">
      <text class="intro-text">
        美食菜谱是一款专注于分享美食制作方法的微信小程序。
        这里汇聚了来自全国各地的美食爱好者，分享他们的独家菜谱和烹饪心得。
        无论您是烹饪新手还是资深大厨，都能在这里找到适合自己的美味佳肴。
      </text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">
      <text class="title-icon">📞</text>
      <text class="title-text">联系我们</text>
    </view>
    
    <view class="contact-list">
      <view class="contact-item" bindtap="callPhone">
        <view class="contact-icon" style="background: #FF6B6B10;">
          <text style="color: #FF6B6B;">📞</text>
        </view>
        <view class="contact-info">
          <text class="contact-label">客服电话</text>
          <text class="contact-value">400-123-4567</text>
        </view>
        <text class="contact-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="contact-item" bindtap="copyWechat">
        <view class="contact-icon" style="background: #4ECDC410;">
          <text style="color: #4ECDC4;">💬</text>
        </view>
        <view class="contact-info">
          <text class="contact-label">官方微信</text>
          <text class="contact-value">caipu_app</text>
        </view>
        <text class="contact-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="contact-item" bindtap="openMap">
        <view class="contact-icon" style="background: #45B7D110;">
          <text style="color: #45B7D1;">📍</text>
        </view>
        <view class="contact-info">
          <text class="contact-label">公司地址</text>
          <text class="contact-value">北京市朝阳区美食大厦12层</text>
        </view>
        <text class="contact-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">
      <text class="title-icon">⚙️</text>
      <text class="title-text">其他</text>
    </view>
    
    <view class="menu-list">
      <view class="menu-item" bindtap="showAgreement">
        <text class="menu-text">用户协议</text>
        <text class="menu-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="menu-item" bindtap="showPrivacy">
        <text class="menu-text">隐私政策</text>
        <text class="menu-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="menu-item" bindtap="checkUpdate">
        <text class="menu-text">检查更新</text>
        <text class="menu-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
      
      <view class="menu-item" bindtap="sendFeedback">
        <text class="menu-text">意见反馈</text>
        <text class="menu-arrow">›</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer">
    <text class="footer-text">{{copyright}}</text>
    <text class="footer-desc">用心做美食，用爱分享</text>
  </view>
</view>
